<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>CSS Card Design</title>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Baloo+Bhai+2&family=Poppins:wght@300&display=swap');
        *{
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
body{
            background-color: bisque;
            padding: 35px;
            margin-left: 16%;
        }
        .card{
            background: url(backimage.jpg);
            width: 900px; 
            height: 700px;
            border-radius: 7px;
            padding: 0 0 34px 0;
            margin: 4px;
            opacity: 1.58;
        }
        
        .image{
            padding: 5px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .image img{
            border-radius: 7px;
            height: 300px;
        }
        .content{
            padding: 6px 12px; 
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
        }
 .content{
            padding: 6px 12px; 
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
        }
       .content h2{
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 35px;
            color:rgb(255, 4, 54);
       }
       .content h3{
            font-size: 24px;
       }
        .content p{
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: normal;
            color: black;
        }
        .content div{
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="card"> 
        <!-- <img src="backimage.jpg" alt=""> -->
        <div class="image">
            <img src="https://t3.ftcdn.net/jpg/05/58/14/66/240_F_558146635_Pjgj1F8Au64JTeB9VGuas0Fm09OhEOGh.jpg" alt="cake">
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h2>🎉🎂 INVITATION 🎂🎉</h2>
            <h3>You're Invited!</h3>
            <p>
                Hello!! <br>
                Today is my birthday and I have organised an event.You are invited in it. <br>
                Please,come and join me as I celebrate another year of life and laughter. Let's make this day extra special with fun, food, and great memories!
            </p> <br>
            <hr>
            <div>
                📅 Date: 31/07/2024 <br>
                ⏰ Time: 8 PM Onward <br>
                📍 Location: KIET College [Main Cafeteria]
            </div> <br>
            <p>Looking forward to sharing this moment with you!</p>
        </div>

    </div>
</body>
 </html>
